title: Journeys With Data
text:
This site is a trail of notes left while wandering through data science, infrastructure, policy, and AI.
Some posts are maps.
Some are sketches.
A few are probably wrong — but hopefully interesting in the attempt.
I write to understand things better, not to look clever. If that sounds like your kind of internet, have a look around.
